            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "Oifaye1",
                    "Sire, we have a visitor.{br}Lord Filat of Belhalla seeks an audience.{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "remove_portrait",
                [
                    "Oifaye1"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "add_portrait",
                [
                    "NobleMan",
                    "Left"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "Sigurd",
                    "Lord Filat, I presume? Thank you for coming.{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "NobleMan",
                    "Lord Sigurd, the Agustrian conflict has escalated into full-scale war, I see.{w}{br}How does this battle look at the moment?{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "Sigurd",
                    "We're faring well so far, somehow, but this hasn't been easy by any means.{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "NobleMan",
                    "Incidentally, Lord Sigurd, I regret to say that I come bearing bad news...{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "Sigurd",
                    "What's happened?{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "NobleMan",
                    "Nasty rumors have emerged of late in the royal court... and they concern you.{w}{br}The rumors claim that, in concert with Quan of Lenster and Eldigan of Nordion,{w}{br}you're conspiring against the crown.{w}{br}This, it is said, is why you're harboring the prince of Isaach in your ranks.{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "Sigurd",
                    "What?! That's absurd! Who in the world could've started such nonsense...{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "NobleMan",
                    "Chancellor Reptor and Duke Langbalt.{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "Sigurd",
                    "I see... I should have known, knowing their disdain for my father.{w}{br}Yet, to take that grudge so far...{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "NobleMan",
                    "Those two are ruled by their envy of your father's immense power,{w}{br}as he is Prince Kurth's only and direct advisor, I'd say.{w}{br}They likely believe a Chalphy-controlled prince{w}{br}will strip them of their influence once he takes the throne.{w}{br}Fear and jealousy dominate their lives...{br}Don't let your guard down against them.{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "Sigurd",
                    "Thank you, sir. I appreciate the warning.{w}{br}By the way, sir... Pray tell, how goes the Isaachian campaign? Is there an end in sight?{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "NobleMan",
                    "It seems there is indeed, from what I've heard.{w}{br}We expect the triumphant return of the prince and your father any day now.{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "Sigurd",
                    "Thank the gods Prince Kurth is safe.{w}{br}Losing him to this war would have dealt such a blow to to Grannvale's future...{w}{br}I know my father worries so much,{w}{br}about how the Belhalla lineage would end with His Majesty's death, unmarried as he is.{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "NobleMan",
                    "Indeed. Before the war started, we tried to hasten him to search for a wife.{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "Sigurd",
                    "If I may, is there a problem?{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "NobleMan",
                    "Indeed... The story behind this has been well known in the royal court for a long time now.{w}{br}Regrettably, His Highness struggles to move on from a long-lost love.{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "Sigurd",
                    "Really? Why did he never marry this person?{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "NobleMan",
                    "Well... Perhaps I ought to tell you the complete tale.{w}{br}This happened some twenty years ago.{w}{br}Prince Kurth had an affair with the duchess of Velthomer,{w}{br}a truly lovely womas as I recall.{w}{br}Duke Victor of Velthomer was...{w}{br}Well, he was a philanderer of the worst degree, and had countless lovers.{w}{br}The prince of course, is nothing like him.{w}{br}He wished only to support the duchess at first, but the two soon fell deeply in love.{w}{br}Victor was distraught, needless to say.{w}{br}He penned a letter denouncing the pair, then he took his own life.{w}{br}The duchess could bear to stay no longer.{w}{br}She fled Grannvale and was never seen again.{w}{br}As I recall, her name was Cigyun.{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "Sigurd",
                    "...Wow. That's horrible...{br}{w}So she was Lord Arvis' mother...{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "NobleMan",
                    "Indeed.{w}{br}I can scarcely imagine what this was like for him...{w}{br}Losing both parents at only the age of seven...{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "Sigurd",
                    "Mm.. And yet, I feel sorry for the prince.{w}{br}Not to mention, for Cigyun as well...{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "NobleMan",
                    "Oh! My apologies.{w}{br}I'm sure a soldier of you caliber has better things to worry about than court gossip.{w}{br}Please, don't worry about the story.{w}{br}You have a war with Agustria to win, after all!{w}{br}Farewell, Lord Sigurd. We look forward to the day that you, too, return to the fatherland in triumph.{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
